content.rendered:
Photo Gallery

Check out some of the recent Wing Chun photos from our students and instructors at Sifu Och Wing Chun in Lakeland, Florida. If you’re a student, be sure to submit your own Wing Chun photos to us so we can include them here! As we learn martial arts in our adult classes and children’s after school programs, we like to post pictures of what our students are doing and how well they are progressing. It’s a fun way to keep tabs on what your friends, kids, and loved ones are doing in our classes…plus you might catch something really cool in the process!
